orld Athletics U20 Championships in 2022, looked to have the height to clear 5.70m and take a big step towards the pole vault finalwhen his manhood got in the way.\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Athletics U20 Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_U20_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 289}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 293, \"to\": 303}, {\"ngram\": \"the height\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"5.70m\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"a big step\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"the pole vault\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"finalwhen\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"his manhood\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The unfortunate incident effectively ended Ammirati's Olympic hopes, with the Frenchman eventually finishing 12th in Group A with a height of 5.60m.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.999997322937761, \"rank\": 1.493240556008927e-06, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The unfortunate incident\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"Ammirati's Olympic hopes\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the Frenchman\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"a height\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"5.60m.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"5.70m was enough for several athletes to advance t